
J Servlet and JSP

Web App: web site where generate the HTML pages are generated dynamically.

Servlet(Interface) java file it can take the request from the client and priovide the responce like a html file.


Creation :
in eclipse open perspective and select Java EE( Servers option will be enabled)

Configuration of Tomcat(web container)
download Tomcat and tomcat documentation-> in server click on the link and choose the apache
 select version-> give location and finish.


how to configure tomacat in eclipse
inside server tab will get an link to add tomact select and select the version, give path finish it

___________________________________________________

What is JSP file?
an HTML page witj some java code
include dynamic content from javacode

it processed on the server

Where to place JSP file:   
goes into Web content folder
must have .jsp extension

_________________________________________
JSP scripting elements:
1. JSP exression: syntax:     <%=some java epression %>
ex: the time on the server is <%= new java.util.Date() %>
 To upper case <%= new String("Hello J").toUpper() %>

2. JSP sciptlet:    <% some java code: 1 to many lines %>.
Inser 1 to many lines of Java code.
to include content in the page use: out.println()


3. JSP Declaration:   <%! variables or method declaration %>
we can declare a method in the jsp
call method n the same jsp


-------------------------------------------------
First time sending the request to server, init method will invoke and servoce method will invoke.

second time sending the request, service method will get invoked,.

Destroy and init method gets invoke only one time.

